{
  "stem": "14613.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the 1,500 to 2,000 people in a barrack were just [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] subjected to inhumane conditions, which means very little food, constant beating, constant-- constant staying on an appell, winter, cold, snow, you're staying without any clothes.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every day, you could see a whole mountain in one corner of the-- of the the barracks, of dead people that did not survive the day.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was just sheer slaughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could be killed for nothing, just because you were standing somewhere and the Kappo or the German just beat you to death for anything you-- you did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't stay properly in a row, they would give you 50 lashes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after 30, you were dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it-- it was a very-- a very dreadful conditions and situation which existed in this-- in this camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Coming from Lodz ghetto, and being thrown immediately in such a condition without a graduating, some-- some kind of a transition period, it was even more pronounced on me than somebody who graduate and went into such a bad condition.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that-- how long I was there, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if anybody asks a question and wants to know, all I can say-- he does not understand the condition.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He cannot visualize the condition, for anyone to think that he could think properly to know how many days or how many weeks he was there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Days didn't count.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know only that, after a while, having been forced there and having no food, I know that one day I maybe was crazy, but I did a desperate thing where I stole a bread.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which, by the way, we did not call stealing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
